OL,3,CTwix advert banned in UK for
OL,4,C'condoning unsafe driving'
OL,6,FAn advert for the chocolate bar Twix
OL,7,Fhas been banned for "condoning unsafe
OL,8,Fdriving", the Advertising Standards
OL,9,FAuthority (ASA) has said.
OL,11,FThe ad, called "Two is More Than One",
OL,12,Fdepicts a man in a car chase driving
OL,13,Foff an empty road, falling down a
OL,14,Frocky hill and landing upside down on
OL,15,Fan identical car's roof.
