OL,6,FThe same man is in both cars, and the
OL,7,Ftop driver hands the lower one a Twix
OL,8,Fthrough the sunroof. The cars then
OL,9,Fdrive off with them both holding the
OL,10,Fgear stick at the same time. The
OL,11,Fcaption, "TWO IS MORE THAN ONE TWIX",
OL,12,Fis shown on the screen.
OL,14,FThe ASA said it received five
OL,15,Fcomplaints about the ads on the
OL,16,Fgrounds that they "encouraged
OL,17,Fdangerous driving and were
OL,18,Firresponsible."
