OL,6,FMars told ITV News: "We always take
OL,7,Fpride in maintaining high standards
OL,8,Facross all our communications and
OL,9,Fevery advert we produce is submitted
OL,10,Ffor approval through the appropriate
OL,11,Freview channels.
OL,13,F"In our view, this particular advert
OL,14,Fadopts a fantastical tone that is
OL,15,Fneither realistic nor intended to be
OL,16,Fimitated.
